These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, reading, camping, singing
1. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking coffee and the person who's hobby is reading##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking coffee##7
4. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea       | milk | coffee        |
| Hobby      | camping  | reading | singing        | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, chinchilla, guinea-pig
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, lacrosse, climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere between the person who's sport is climbing and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | chinchilla | fish       | guinea-pig         | turtle     |
| Sport   | lacrosse   | soccer | climbing | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, family, western, sports
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, punk, r&b, gospel
1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the fan of punk and the fan of folk##7
3. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the fan of folk is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the person watching family movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | sports | western | romance  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | folk  | gospel   | punk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, sudoku, puzzles, photography
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, soccer, tennis, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's hobby is photography##7
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | sudoku | drawing | photography       | puzzles |
| Sport   | soccer      | swimming   | tennis | sailing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, cooking, skydiving, hiking
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, thai, mexican, turkish
1. the turkish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
2. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the turkish is somewhere between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
5. the turkish is on the left of the mexican##1
6. the thai is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | woodworking   | hiking | cooking |
| Nationality   | japanese      | thai | turkish      | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, cola, lemonade
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, polish, italian, canadian
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the italian##1
2. the italian is the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the polish is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the canadian##3
6. the canadian is somewhere between the mexican and the polish##7
7. the italian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee | milk      | cola | lemonade     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | canadian | polish   | italian |

