.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, nectarine, spinach, cranberry
There are 4 different nationalities: german, egyptian, colombian, turkish
1. the german is on the far left##1
2. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the egyptian##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
4. the turkish is somewhere between the person eating banana and the person eating spinach##7
5. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person eating spinach##5
6. the turkish is on the left or right of the colombian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | cranberry    | banana   | nectarine | spinach  |
| Nationality   | german | colombian | turkish    | egyptian |

