.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, malaysian, mexican, japanese
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, turtle, guinea-pig
1. the malaysian is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
3. the japanese is the owner of the turtle##1
4. the mexican is somewhere between the japanese and the turkish##7
5. the malaysian is on the left of the turkish##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | japanese | mexican | malaysian | turkish |
| Pet           | turtle   | guinea-pig    | ferret       | goat  |

