.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, bartender, librarian, entrepreneur
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, punk, trance, gospel
1. the paramedic is not the fan of disco##6
2. the librarian is on the right of the paramedic##1
3. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
4. the paramedic is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
5. the librarian is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the bartender##7
6. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | entrepreneur | paramedic | librarian | bartender |
| Music-Genre   | gospel         | trance      | disco | punk            |

