.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, romance, superhero, zombie
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, goldfish, frog
1. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the owner of the frog##7
2. the person watching romance movies is not the owner of the goldfish##6
3. the owner of the hamster is not the person watching superhero movies##6
4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
5. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the cat##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | zombie | romance | superhero |
| Pet           | cat    | hamster   | frog  | goldfish      |

