.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, western, adventure, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, indie, reggae, punk
1. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the fan of pop##5
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of indie is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching horror movies is between the person watching western movies and the fan of indie##2
6. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the fan of indie and the person watching western movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | horror | western | adventure   |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | reggae      | pop      | punk |

