4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is baking##7

.:: Answer ::.
