.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, dancing, card-games, magic-tricks
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, taxi, helicopter, car
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the person driving the taxi##6
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
6. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | magic-tricks | cooking | dancing | card-games |
| Transport   | boat   | car      | taxi        | helicopter  |

