.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, hot-chocolate, 7up
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, rock, trance, dubstep
1. the fan of rock is in an even position##4
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the fan of trance##7
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
4. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the fan of trance##1
7. the person drinking tea is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | sprite   | hot-chocolate | tea | 7up   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | trance   | dubstep | rock |

