.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, chinchilla, fish, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane, helicopter, car
1. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
5. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | chinchilla    | fish | rat     | turtle |
| Transport   | helicopter | car  | airplane | jet-ski |

 